                            <comment id="15284684" author="tallison@mitre.org" created="Mon, 16 May 2016 14:59:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We can fix this by adding this to our mime-types.xml file:&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;match value=&quot;Delivered-To:&quot; type=&quot;string&quot; offset=&quot;0&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

